which is ‘silver’ from the word “Blue Silver Plant”.

48
00:05:40,980 --> 00:05:46,350
<i>I planned to deflate the Double Star of Hao Tian.</i>

49
00:05:46,350 --> 00:05:49,180
<i>But I’ve never expected the Blue Silver Plant</i>

50
00:05:49,180 --> 00:05:52,520
<i>to be so powerful.</i>

51
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:55,020
<i>That surprised me.</i>

52
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:09,370
Later, we became sworn brothers and sister.

53
00:06:09,370 --> 00:06:12,810
Ah Yin was the youngest and
ranked the third among us.

54
00:06:12,810 --> 00:06:16,440
We called her Ah Yin or Little San.

55
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:19,370
This is where your name derives.

56
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:26,100
Both my elder brother and I
fell for Ah Yin, the pretty lady.

57
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:35,480
Elder Brother dropped out in the end
and returned to the tribe.

58
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:38,980
On the same night,

59
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,570
Ah Yin confessed to me that

60
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:50,020
she was a Century Millennium Soul Beast,
Blue Silver Emperor.

61
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:59,790
However, my love for her surpassed everything.

62
00:07:04,410 --> 00:07:07,320
I didn’t care about her identity at all!

63
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:13,570
As long as she could enter the mature period,
she would become a human.

64
00:07:14,350 --> 00:07:19,730
So, I expressed my love to her.

65
00:07:19,730 --> 00:07:23,300
Only then did I know that
she had always loved me.

66
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:27,380
She was worried that
Elder Brother might be upset,

67
00:07:27,380 --> 00:07:29,650
so she didn’t take any action.

68
00:07:29,650 --> 00:07:33,230
Since then, we got together.

69
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:36,110
I thought we could live happily ever after.

70
00:07:36,110 --> 00:07:39,410
As we were going to return to the tribe,

71
00:07:39,410 --> 00:07:43,550
