found out about Ah Yin’s identity...

72
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:46,320
We managed to get rid of them,

73
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,980
so they went to Hao Tian Tribe.

74
00:07:50,320 --> 00:07:54,780
Your grandpa was already very sick then
so the news let to his death.

75
00:07:55,860 --> 00:07:58,770
Elder Brother succeeded as
the chief of the tribe.

76
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:03,520
However, he struggled among the powers.

77
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:12,000
The day that you were born
was destined to be a special day.

78
00:08:12,990 --> 00:08:18,510
That day, my soul power reached Level 90.

79
00:08:18,510 --> 00:08:20,160
And your mom

80
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:23,340
