82
00:08:34,070 --> 00:08:36,120
Are you willing to sacrifice?

83
00:08:36,130 --> 00:08:38,710
Do you know you will vanish forever for using it?

84
00:08:38,710 --> 00:08:42,850
Ah Yin, no. Please go with them.
Don’t sacrifice.

85
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:45,060
Stop her, everyone.

86
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:47,760
Blue Silver Plant has never had a home.

87
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:52,000
After so many ordeals, I’ve finally met you.

88
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:55,900
